cu.explanation_en: Setting phy_log_level to an unknown enum 'invalid' will cause configuration parsing failure and prevent the gNB CU from starting properly.

du.explanation_en: Setting phy_log_level to an unknown enum 'invalid' will cause configuration parsing failure and prevent the gNB DU from starting properly.
du.explanation_zh: 將 phy_log_level 設定為未知的枚舉值 'invalid' 會導致配置解析失敗，並阻止 gNB DU 正確啟動。
